Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.46,0:00:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.66,0:00:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.13,0:00:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.67,0:00:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.78,0:00:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.99,0:00:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.79,0:00:54.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.07,0:01:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.51,0:01:10.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.18,0:01:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.82,0:01:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.52,0:01:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.09,0:01:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要讓我下去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.43,0:01:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙漠鋼彈!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.97,0:01:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你，我的沙漠鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.93,0:01:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十八話\N[破壞托爾吉斯]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.45,0:02:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些技師的來歷知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.65,0:02:20.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全部嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.38,0:02:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們果然是本來曾參予
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.69,0:02:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為OZ開發機動戰士的技師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.06,0:02:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.03,0:02:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開發托爾吉斯途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.69,0:02:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正確來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.93,0:02:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在完成了托爾吉斯的設計圖後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.16,0:02:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5人就全部失蹤，下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.73,0:02:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托爾吉斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.47,0:02:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是傑克斯特校使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.20,0:02:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人稱原型里歐的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.67,0:02:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然是20年前設計出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.71,0:02:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在地球仍是最強的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.38,0:02:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最強這個形容詞不適當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.62,0:02:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最強的是要讓所有士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.02,0:02:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它當作自己的榮耀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.96,0:03:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫他們製造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.26,0:03:03.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托爾吉斯，不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.86,0:03:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝過鋼彈的最強機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.71,0:03:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長，我把傑克斯特校帶來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.85,0:03:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地方狹窄對不起，請坐在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.15,0:03:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯特校不需要那種待遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.45,0:03:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,退下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你不自在，對不起，傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.66,0:03:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你不要介意，特列斯大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.70,0:03:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已準備上軍事法庭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.97,0:03:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，如果你今後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.94,0:03:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也肯為羅姆斐拉財團出力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,法庭就不會那麼為難你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出力?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團很在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.28,0:03:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在地上最強的機動戰士鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.22,0:03:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你今後也願意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.65,0:04:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為打倒鋼彈的騎士作戰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.72,0:04:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人，很遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.09,0:04:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能遵從羅姆斐拉財團的意願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.39,0:04:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.69,0:04:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈憑著戰爭時不須要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.96,0:04:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個人感情在戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.93,0:04:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和鋼彈的戰鬥已經完結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.04,0:04:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?那麼，傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.11,0:04:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就為了OZ犧牲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.68,0:04:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你受審被判有罪會對OZ有害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光榮戰死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.65,0:04:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才會令眾多士兵為你哀悼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.48,0:04:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令他們擁有更激昂的鬥志
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.49,0:04:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團\N的高層當然也會同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.32,0:04:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閃電伯爵的稱號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.16,0:04:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會成為傳說中的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.29,0:04:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.63,0:04:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的死有那麼大的價值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你死後就會自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.17,0:04:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永別了，傑克斯‧馬吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.08,0:04:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在所有人離去後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.94,0:05:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,50部艾亞利玆和20部坎沙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.08,0:05:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就會攻擊這艘艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.85,0:05:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對手是想巴結財團的聯合餘黨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.18,0:05:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然任務是瞞過財團高層耳目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.02,0:05:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放走傑克斯特校你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.62,0:05:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但把你當作敵人\N我覺得太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.43,0:05:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯，這是身為特列斯的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,活下去的考驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使我想做甚麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.40,0:05:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也瞞不過特列斯的心嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,模擬戰開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.16,0:05:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是MD系統嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.63,0:05:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於用開發的是舊型里歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以要從機外輸入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.30,0:05:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在宇宙用MD陶拉斯上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.13,0:05:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就毫無問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.80,0:05:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,性能很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.60,0:06:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD足以增強兵力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.41,0:06:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茲巴洛夫技師長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，代替士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.61,0:06:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為主要軍力的日子亦不遠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.48,0:06:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.61,0:06:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人正攻擊這裡!他沒答話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.95,0:06:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!剛好作為MD的目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫它們攻擊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.19,0:06:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知死活的敵人間諜嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.93,0:06:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人里歐有通訊進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.93,0:06:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯特校?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.93,0:06:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊中止!中止!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.17,0:06:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想代表血肉之驅的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.24,0:06:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,挑戰MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想死嗎?特列斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.08,0:06:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD不會像人類般留情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.18,0:06:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果MD是優秀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.91,0:06:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就不須要存在於這世上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.38,0:06:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想在這裡\N分出高下，通話完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.32,0:06:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他瘋了嗎? 不要緊，攻擊特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.39,0:06:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.23,0:06:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是命令，他想殺死我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.93,0:06:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊，動手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.03,0:07:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不!我做不到!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.60,0:07:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由我來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.30,0:07:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你停止!技師長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.64,0:07:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.17,0:07:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是特列斯‧克修里那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死茲巴洛夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們…?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.39,0:07:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停…停手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.72,0:07:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遵照特列斯特校的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.49,0:07:27.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們要當場把你槍決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.39,0:07:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你完了，茲巴洛夫技師長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.79,0:07:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是駕駛機動戰士戰鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.63,0:07:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是戰爭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.33,0:07:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們勝利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解除命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.47,0:07:41.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,操縱MD\N和士兵的也是人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.64,0:07:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你多一點讚賞和愛惜人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.65,0:07:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯，快點回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.02,0:07:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有你，OZ會容許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.72,0:07:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無用的人做出無禮的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了!是穿過OZ監視的穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.67,0:08:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.03,0:08:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這條航路OZ較少使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.40,0:08:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，我們能俘虜鋼彈了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.67,0:08:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正確來說是鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.04,0:08:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,朝著這裡來的穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.68,0:08:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是用來搬運機動戰士的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.84,0:08:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，拘留那士兵做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.55,0:08:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鋼彈的駕駛員是為了和OZ戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.08,0:08:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才回來宇宙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.05,0:08:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有相同的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.12,0:08:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要和那駕駛員交涉聯手抗敵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.79,0:08:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以把那駕駛員交給OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.13,0:08:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確保我們自身的安全嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.76,0:08:42.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和把偷襲當作上策的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.70,0:08:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,普通交涉根本不會有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.57,0:08:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只有和OZ全面戰鬥一途!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.64,0:08:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高速機急速接近這裡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.81,0:08:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信是OZ的機動戰士陶拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.38,0:08:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5部嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.65,0:08:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有20部宇宙里歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.51,0:08:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能打贏!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.45,0:08:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我應該說過別輕視OZ!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.38,0:09:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ知道這一帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.45,0:09:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藏有聯合宇宙軍的殘餘中隊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.69,0:09:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們只是用5部陶拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.79,0:09:10.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就來攻擊聯合的殘餘部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.43,0:09:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別把鋼彈的駕駛員交給他們!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.73,0:09:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合的機動戰士分散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.53,0:09:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.90,0:09:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有飛行物體接近後退了的部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.67,0:09:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.81,0:09:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們發現了\N從地球來的鋼彈嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.74,0:09:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前來迎擊的全是普通型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙戰用里歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.71,0:09:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!把它們設定為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.25,0:09:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MD的攻擊目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡交給你，我去追穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.94,0:09:54.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到是無人開動的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.84,0:09:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在毫無障礙物的宇宙裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.17,0:09:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們認為那是有效的武器吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.71,0:10:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不污染自己雙手的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.81,0:10:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這已經是遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.28,0:10:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發動戰爭的人類是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.42,0:10:09.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在戰鬥裡流的血不會白流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.12,0:10:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愚蠢的人類看見那些血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.19,0:10:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少許也好，他們也能反省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.82,0:10:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但淪為遊戲的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.66,0:10:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會成為娛樂的工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.66,0:10:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒不如用遊戲分出勝負就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.43,0:10:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，誰也不用死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.07,0:10:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果對手也有那種技術就是遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.47,0:10:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並非沒有技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.24,0:10:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了用自身感覺戰爭的責任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.24,0:10:32.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們才不給予自動機能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.18,0:10:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們能給予嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.68,0:10:37.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，你們就能活得久一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.51,0:10:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不能製造呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.92,0:10:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果要做那種事，死掉更好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.09,0:10:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然年輕人認為合理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.16,0:10:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但發動戰爭並不合理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.36,0:10:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本來想叫你們製造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.89,0:10:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比你們的托爾吉斯和鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.46,0:10:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有更高性能的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.27,0:10:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死我們吧，我們不會協助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.14,0:11:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不痛苦亦不後悔的戰爭遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.21,0:11:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,談判決裂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.21,0:11:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校!尼哥爾特尉有聯絡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.45,0:11:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼事?尼哥爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.65,0:11:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校\N我接收到聯合的無線電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.05,0:11:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想和鋼彈的駕駛員聯手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.65,0:11:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.42,0:11:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊!把一切毀滅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.22,0:11:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.67,0:11:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.15,0:11:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一瞬間消滅了5部嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.29,0:11:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人機動戰士加速前去8時方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.93,0:11:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是甚麼怪物!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.27,0:12:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經消滅聯合的主力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即奪取穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.44,0:12:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奪取?別做無謂的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.21,0:12:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們根本不需要\N沒有鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.11,0:12:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.92,0:12:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.08,0:12:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把通訊系統借給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.25,0:12:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.63,0:12:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是卡特爾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.10,0:12:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回到宇宙的同伴啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.90,0:12:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起保護衛星吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.77,0:12:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在使用希洛的線路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.67,0:12:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是個優秀的士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.98,0:12:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他有團結5名鋼彈駕駛員的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.15,0:12:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡是…卡特爾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.79,0:12:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回到宇宙的同伴啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.82,0:13:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起保護衛星吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.23,0:13:05.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止毀滅穿梭機!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.63,0:13:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你原來有可憐部下的心嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.73,0:13:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就好說話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.97,0:13:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是為OZ製造鋼彈吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.11,0:13:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你們製造
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.81,0:13:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以勝過鋼彈的機動戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.32,0:13:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個少年就是鋼彈的駕駛員嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.96,0:13:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長，所有陶拉斯正朝著這邊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.89,0:13:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.43,0:13:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能盡量離開穿梭機作戰嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.06,0:13:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.20,0:13:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓你死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.87,0:13:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中止攻擊穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.47,0:13:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陶拉斯部隊離開穿梭機的航路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.87,0:14:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?中止攻擊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即是放走穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.78,0:14:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它在宇宙漂浮是它的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.25,0:14:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但航路上的垃圾一定要清除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.32,0:14:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼哥爾，毀滅它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.59,0:14:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙里歐交給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.92,0:14:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去毀滅穿梭機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿梭機仍然毫無動靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.08,0:14:34.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我開始打掃航路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.58,0:14:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.55,0:14:42.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿梭機攻擊里歐?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.59,0:14:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿梭機還能航行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.95,0:14:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全體追擊!毀滅它!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.59,0:14:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在的我們沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.53,0:14:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能和OZ對抗的力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.77,0:15:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…那個駕駛員做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.91,0:15:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望我的計謀能得到回報就好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.62,0:15:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對…大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.99,0:15:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起…保護宇宙吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.87,0:15:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來接你的直升機嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.44,0:15:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.44,0:15:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托爾吉斯的修理如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.47,0:15:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全靠你的部下，修理得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.64,0:15:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.95,0:15:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後方4030方向有雷達反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.21,0:15:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了嗎?好準時啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.65,0:15:51.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這艘艦會被擊沉，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.19,0:15:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你盡情戰鬥，雖然心情很複雜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.16,0:15:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，特校，請你一定要贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.93,0:15:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多謝你的照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.53,0:16:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出擊了，托爾吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.50,0:16:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾亞利玆50部!坎沙20部!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要証明給他們看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.08,0:16:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們太輕視我的性命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.71,0:17:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有多少部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.30,0:17:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很有決心!\N但我還不可以死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.68,0:18:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯!別那麼執著!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.63,0:18:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是不想回應\N無謂的期望嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.66,0:18:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的友情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.86,0:18:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直至面具碎掉為止啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.33,0:18:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯，我不能成為你的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,永別了，特列斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.47,0:18:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太陽系內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.67,0:19:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生物能奇蹟地生活繁殖的惑星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.24,0:19:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.55,0:19:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.71,0:19:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在衛星開發上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.32,0:19:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類憑著豐富的資源和技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.52,0:19:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得到新的大地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.49,0:19:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，那只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.42,0:19:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,模擬地球那片母親大地的空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.23,0:19:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,製造衛星有甚麼意義呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說它的主要目的是開發技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.27,0:19:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令地球的人類過得豐裕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.41,0:19:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類在這些模擬空間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.47,0:19:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有無理的要求吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.11,0:19:37.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己的生命\N不會受到大自然威脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.38,0:19:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有比地球高的穩定性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.38,0:19:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有停頓的發展\N好像答應了人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.32,0:19:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓其永遠生存下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.66,0:19:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙有容許由零開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.39,0:19:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而陶醉的時代吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.76,0:19:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但衛星…不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.73,0:19:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類能夠忘記地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星的技術開發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.21,0:20:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為地球帶來了甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.84,0:20:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球最想要的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.94,0:20:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是軍事力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.55,0:20:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破壞是人類不能拋棄的精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.62,0:20:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在衛星正不斷擁有軍事技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.65,0:20:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們不能忘記地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.86,0:20:22.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球的美麗是偉大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.33,0:20:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擁有強大力量名為人類的動物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.49,0:20:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也想管理一個惑星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.63,0:20:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在惑星之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.30,0:20:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生物的生存是剎那間的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.87,0:20:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是短暫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.47,0:20:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類能想到的始終…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.24,0:20:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毫無改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.28,0:20:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人類飛出宇宙的歲月是白費的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.25,0:20:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在現實面前，理想只是夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.68,0:20:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虛假的生活空間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.65,0:20:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虛假的和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.75,0:20:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙只是孕育更多戰爭的溫床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.26,0:20:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰爭會奪去很多生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.69,0:21:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然人類從未\N忘記過戰爭的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.77,0:21:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但他們絕對不想停止戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.47,0:21:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,流下的血和淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.37,0:21:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是儀式的裝飾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.04,0:21:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,時代裡只有用戰爭講述的歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.44,0:21:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為和平而戰這等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.35,0:21:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,經過修飾的漂亮話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.05,0:21:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是過去多次被高呼的名句吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.72,0:21:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星為了和平而擁有軍備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.86,0:21:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和地球毫無分別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.62,0:21:30.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以他們能加入成為同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.60,0:21:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藉著流很多血，活下去…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.76,0:21:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到此為止吧，迪歐‧麥斯威爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.70,0:21:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停止那題目吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.47,0:21:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強迫大家不安不大好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.31,0:21:43.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轉校後和大家這樣打招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.01,0:21:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教師我認為有點問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.94,0:21:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，迪歐同學\N你坐在最後一行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.48,0:21:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼，人類為何要戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.89,0:21:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥裡或許有存在的意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.02,0:22:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥的人類有充實感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.29,0:22:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且，戰鬥的人類不會腐敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.03,0:22:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.40,0:22:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.72,0:22:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.72,0:22:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.72,0:22:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.72,0:22:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.22,0:22:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.72,0:23:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.22,0:23:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.72,0:23:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.72,0:23:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.41,0:23:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次回預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.55,0:23:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降落衛星的鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.08,0:23:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有讚美也沒有獎賞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.02,0:23:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們只有消滅OZ的任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.36,0:23:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死神鋼彈和陶拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.92,0:23:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在宇宙空間戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.23,0:23:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，迪歐戰敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.99,0:23:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成為OZ的俘虜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.66,0:23:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛為了保守秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.47,0:23:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前去殺死迪歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.70,0:23:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新機動戰記-鋼彈W，第十九話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.67,0:23:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強襲巴爾吉

